author: Ryan George Extra Plus!
description:
Disney parks! The happiest places on Earth… with the highest concentration of mobility scooters per square mile. But look, beneath the Mickey-shaped pretzels and overpriced corn dogs, there’s a lot of weird stuff going on.

So yeah, it turns out the most magical place on earth is also kinda the weirdest. But don’t worry — I looked into all this, got distracted by a TikTok meerkat, argued with my wife mid-video, and still managed to bring you the secrets Disney doesn’t exactly put on the brochures.

Anyway, watch the video, learn some cursed facts, and then try not to think about them next time you’re standing in line for Space Mountain.

👍 Like the video, subscribe for more nonsense, and leave a comment with your favorite weird Disney fact (or your favorite ash-scattering technique — no actually don’t do that).

#Disney #RyanGeorge #ThemeParkSecrets
